gw.api.restriction

Class UnionRestriction<T extends KeyableBean>

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.restriction.UnionRestriction<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type of the entities for the restriction.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Restriction<T>

    public final class UnionRestriction<T extends KeyableBean>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Restriction<T>
    Disjunctive restriction composed of a pair of sub-restrictions. The restrictions will be evaluated in order when applied to in-memory collections, and filtering will also short-circuit if the first restriction passes.
